{"tid":653250,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打有趕走狗公嘅經驗","createTime":"2018-05-04T14:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-05T02:17:56.000Z","uid":32298,"like":5,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"85e970e9ed6ff8e9fa2827e0373e665e252084fd","tid":653250,"uid":32298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟同女朋友由中學就識，近呢半年開始拍拖。據我所知一直都有幾日狗公纏住佢（大約三四隻），自從佢拍左拖之後俾我話得多佢都已經無乜點同啲狗公傾計。<br />\n<br />\n但最近，又有一隻狗公（之前果三四隻入面嘅其中一隻）搵返我女朋友，借溝我女朋友身邊啲fd為名義，成日搵我女朋友傾偈，同埋條仆街真係好撚嘔心，以前都已經間唔中又送下野俾我女朋友（好似送過唇膏果d），又成日借啲意肢體接觸咁（摸下頭果d，唔係私人部位）。最近又俾我見到佢成日cap鳩佢同我條女啲對話上ig，我屌佢老母仲要厚顏無恥到話我條女啲女仔fd都成日咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想問各位巴打有無經驗，可以趕走隻柒頭狗公？<br />\n<br />\nPs. 我同我女朋友感情好好，佢都對我好坦白，個狗公搵佢佢都會話我知，所以唔洗擔心我綠帽。我係純粹覺得個狗公好撚嘔心，希望各位幫我諗諗計，趕走隻狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7980ee351e0889595bf172a63bcf46bc78ea831","tid":653250,"uid":32298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Btw 狗公，你老母俾狗屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8aecaea6de64e8d120968660ff8b644d3751cd6a","tid":653250,"uid":141435,"like":10,"dislike":8,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T14:19:16.000Z","msg":"少年 要走嘅始終都會走。留得低就係緣份。<br